ally lives underwater. When it comes onto land in search of food, it takes water with it in the form of a bubble on its head."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "It crawls onto the land in search of food. Its water bubble allows it to breathe and protects its soft head."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "It forms a water bubble at the rear of its body and then covers its head with it. Meeting another Dewpider means comparing water-bubble sizes."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "It can only breathe oxygen that has dissolved in water, so it wears a water bubble on its head when it walks around on land."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "When two Dewpider meet, they display their water bubbles to each other. Then the one with the smaller bubble gets out of the other\u2019s way."}], "entryGameVersions": ["moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "dewpider"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "araquanid"}]}